1
00:00:02,035 --> 00:00:04,704
Narrator: With the detonation
of miniature Rose

2
00:00:04,771 --> 00:00:08,908
activated by the stopping
of his heart, netero perished,

3
00:00:08,976 --> 00:00:13,113
and when he died,
the king died along with him.

4
00:00:14,181 --> 00:00:16,116
( Both wailing )

5
00:00:24,791 --> 00:00:25,725
♪

6
00:00:25,792 --> 00:00:27,727
( Singing in Japanese )

7
00:01:09,169 --> 00:01:11,104
♪

8
00:01:14,808 --> 00:01:19,079
Royal guards: Sire!

9
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:21,715
( Flesh cracks )

10
00:01:21,782 --> 00:01:22,883
( Both gasp )

11
00:01:27,187 --> 00:01:29,122
( Menthuthuyoupi gasps )

12
00:01:29,189 --> 00:01:31,091
( Shaiapouf gasps )

13
00:01:32,326 --> 00:01:33,494
He’s breathing!

14
00:01:34,928 --> 00:01:36,329
Menthuthuyoupi:
We have to hurry!

15
00:01:36,396 --> 00:01:39,099
Damn it!
The king doesn’t have long!

16
00:01:39,166 --> 00:01:41,335
This is bad!

17
00:01:41,401 --> 00:01:44,738
And there’s not enough time
to get him back to pitou!

18
00:01:49,042 --> 00:01:50,810
Shaiapouf:
It’s going to be fine.

19
00:01:50,878 --> 00:01:53,848
I will save the king myself.

20
00:01:53,914 --> 00:01:55,315
Menthuthuyoupi: But how?

21
00:02:02,022 --> 00:02:04,024
Shaiapouf:
I will let him consume me.

22
00:02:04,091 --> 00:02:08,329
Yes, it’s as simple as that.

23
00:02:08,395 --> 00:02:10,297
( Menthuthuyoupi gasps )

24
00:02:17,404 --> 00:02:19,339
♪

25
00:02:21,408 --> 00:02:25,412
Shaiapouf: Hear me!
Listen closely, my cells!

26
00:02:25,479 --> 00:02:29,883
Go! Permeate the king,
and heal him!

27
00:03:01,381 --> 00:03:03,016
( Menthuthuyoupi gasps )

28
00:03:04,818 --> 00:03:07,087
♪

29
00:03:22,836 --> 00:03:23,937
( Meruem gasps )

30
00:03:24,004 --> 00:03:25,939
( Shuddering )

31
00:03:28,408 --> 00:03:30,143
Both: Sire!

32
00:03:37,818 --> 00:03:39,119
Shaiapouf: Sire!

33
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:42,089
Are you all right?

34
00:03:42,155 --> 00:03:44,124
How do you feel?

35
00:03:47,127 --> 00:03:50,897
Meruem: An exquisite delicacy
beyond description.

36
00:03:52,366 --> 00:03:56,470
It feels like i’m breathing
the air of paradise.

37
00:03:56,537 --> 00:03:59,306
I can feel my energy.

38
00:03:59,373 --> 00:04:02,109
It’s flooding back into me...

39
00:04:03,410 --> 00:04:07,414
Like some enchanted fairy mist.

40
00:04:09,016 --> 00:04:12,152
Shaiapouf: No, please.

41
00:04:14,755 --> 00:04:19,693
I am not worthy of praise
such as this, my king!

42
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:21,695
( Groaning )

43
00:04:21,762 --> 00:04:23,030
( Menthuthuyoupi gasps )

44
00:04:23,096 --> 00:04:25,065
( Shaiapouf panting )

45
00:04:26,934 --> 00:04:29,770
I’m very happy
to hear that, sire.

46
00:04:29,837 --> 00:04:32,039
( Breathing deeply )

47
00:04:32,105 --> 00:04:35,475
Please feast
until your heart is content.

48
00:04:35,542 --> 00:04:38,378
There’s plenty more
where that came from.

49
00:04:42,850 --> 00:04:45,920
Meruem: This is far too good.

50
00:04:45,986 --> 00:04:51,425
And now that I have
experienced this taste,

51
00:04:51,491 --> 00:04:54,728
i’ll never, ever be able

52
00:04:54,795 --> 00:04:58,299
to eat anything else
but that in my life.

53
00:04:59,933 --> 00:05:02,436
( Shaiapouf wails )

54
00:05:05,072 --> 00:05:08,342
Ohh! Sire!

55
00:05:08,408 --> 00:05:11,878
Sire! Oh, sire!

56
00:05:11,945 --> 00:05:14,714
Please, please, no more!

57
00:05:14,781 --> 00:05:18,218
This heavenly bliss,
I can’t take any more of it!

58
00:05:18,285 --> 00:05:20,354
Please, stop!

59
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:22,188
No more!

60
00:05:22,256 --> 00:05:24,191
( Gasping )

61
00:05:27,361 --> 00:05:30,331
Sire!

62
00:05:32,533 --> 00:05:34,301
Menthuthuyoupi:
Oh, please, sire,

63
00:05:34,368 --> 00:05:38,005
I sincerely hope you’ll be
willing to accept this as well.

64
00:05:41,942 --> 00:05:43,877
♪

65
00:05:43,944 --> 00:05:46,046
( Grunts )

66
00:05:52,152 --> 00:05:54,254
( Grunts )

67
00:06:06,834 --> 00:06:09,003
Shaiapouf:
He’s liquefying his cells.

68
00:06:12,339 --> 00:06:15,409
Smart, youpi. Very smart.

69
00:06:16,510 --> 00:06:18,445
( Meruem gasping )

70
00:06:20,514 --> 00:06:22,449
( Dripping )

71
00:06:40,968 --> 00:06:44,905
What rich and powerful
depth of flavor.

72
00:06:44,972 --> 00:06:49,310
This could only have come
from the heavens above,

73
00:06:49,376 --> 00:06:53,046
these veritable dewdrops
of the angels.

74
00:06:54,848 --> 00:06:56,917
( Menthuthuyoupi groans )

75
00:07:01,755 --> 00:07:03,390
Sire!

76
00:07:03,457 --> 00:07:06,694
( Wails ) Sire!

77
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:10,264
Oh, sire!

78
00:07:14,301 --> 00:07:15,836
( Shaiapouf gasping )

79
00:07:17,304 --> 00:07:22,810
Meruem: Try as I might,
I cannot compare the two.

80
00:07:22,876 --> 00:07:26,446
I will declare
without hesitation

81
00:07:26,513 --> 00:07:29,850
both of them are supreme dishes.

82
00:07:29,917 --> 00:07:31,852
( Shaiapouf gasps )

83
00:07:31,919 --> 00:07:33,854
( Menthuthuyoupi sighs )

84
00:07:33,921 --> 00:07:38,392
Meruem: I need more,
more of both.

85
00:07:38,458 --> 00:07:40,860
Give me all that you have...

86
00:07:41,995 --> 00:07:44,364
And I will receive it,

87
00:07:44,431 --> 00:07:47,034
so give me more of it.

88
00:07:52,873 --> 00:07:56,243
Menthuthuyoupi: Sire!

89
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:59,280
Shaiapouf: Sire!

90
00:07:59,346 --> 00:08:00,981
Menthuthuyoupi: Yes!

91
00:08:02,115 --> 00:08:03,383
Shaiapouf: Sire!

92
00:08:05,485 --> 00:08:07,787
Both: With pleasure!

93
00:08:09,056 --> 00:08:11,325
Narrator:
This was supreme bliss

94
00:08:11,391 --> 00:08:14,327
and unparalleled joy.

95
00:08:40,420 --> 00:08:41,922
Shaiapouf: What is this?

96
00:08:43,423 --> 00:08:45,425
Menthuthuyoupi:
What’s this feeling?

97
00:08:49,963 --> 00:08:53,934
Meruem:
From this point on always,

98
00:08:54,001 --> 00:08:56,470
you will refer to me
as meruem.

99
00:08:56,537 --> 00:08:58,239
( Both gasp )

100
00:09:04,378 --> 00:09:08,349
Meruem: For you see,
that name...

101
00:09:08,415 --> 00:09:10,817
Is the name my mother gave me.

102
00:09:10,884 --> 00:09:12,819
( Chorus vocalizing )

103
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:18,325
( Shaiapouf gasping )

104
00:09:20,394 --> 00:09:22,396
Menthuthuyoupi: I see now.

105
00:09:23,897 --> 00:09:25,699
Royal guards: So this is...

106
00:09:25,766 --> 00:09:27,101
( Chorus continues )

107
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:39,846
Unconditional love!

108
00:09:49,423 --> 00:09:53,294
Narrator: By facing the king’s
near-death and revival

109
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:57,064
and sharing the essence
of their own being,

110
00:09:57,130 --> 00:10:00,867
pouf and youpi
underwent a transformation...

111
00:10:02,269 --> 00:10:05,773
And became equals to the queen,

112
00:10:05,839 --> 00:10:08,975
the mother of their species.

113
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:18,318
( Wind rushing )

114
00:10:39,139 --> 00:10:41,041
♪

115
00:10:51,151 --> 00:10:53,687
Menthuthuyoupi: It’s clear
that his strength has increased.

116
00:10:53,754 --> 00:10:56,890
He’s even stronger than before!

117
00:10:56,957 --> 00:11:00,694
Shaiapouf: It appears that
our flesh was of help to him.

118
00:11:00,761 --> 00:11:04,632
We are a part of him now.

119
00:11:04,698 --> 00:11:08,635
What an honor this is,
what supreme bliss!

120
00:11:08,702 --> 00:11:11,838
Menthuthuyoupi: The king’s
heartbeat, his warmth.

121
00:11:11,905 --> 00:11:16,042
We’re even able to share
in the king’s thoughts.

122
00:11:16,109 --> 00:11:17,711
( Sighs )

123
00:11:17,778 --> 00:11:19,713
Oh?

124
00:11:21,915 --> 00:11:23,216
However...

125
00:11:24,885 --> 00:11:28,822
Shaiapouf: Because of that,
we can tell...

126
00:11:28,889 --> 00:11:30,624
The king is currently...

127
00:11:33,227 --> 00:11:35,663
Both: Extremely confused.

128
00:11:41,001 --> 00:11:42,636
Your highness.

129
00:11:45,172 --> 00:11:47,975
Menthuthuyoupi:
Uh, l-lord meruem,

130
00:11:48,041 --> 00:11:49,643
how are you feeling, sire?

131
00:11:49,710 --> 00:11:50,945
Is everything all right?

132
00:11:53,647 --> 00:11:56,950
Maybe we should go back
to the palace first, sire.

133
00:11:58,652 --> 00:12:00,821
Shaiapouf:
If you still wish to feed,

134
00:12:00,888 --> 00:12:03,591
there is more than enough
to satisfy you.

135
00:12:05,092 --> 00:12:08,696
The rest of me will arrive
in just a few more minutes.

136
00:12:10,130 --> 00:12:11,164
Meruem: Feed?

137
00:12:12,332 --> 00:12:13,867
Oh, I see.

138
00:12:13,934 --> 00:12:16,703
♪

139
00:12:16,770 --> 00:12:19,673
That taste was real after all.

140
00:12:20,807 --> 00:12:23,743
( Both gasp )

141
00:12:23,810 --> 00:12:27,213
Meruem: Even as I wandered
through the waning light,

142
00:12:27,281 --> 00:12:30,584
I heard someone call my name.

143
00:12:32,119 --> 00:12:35,089
"Meruem," they said.

144
00:12:35,155 --> 00:12:37,724
- ( Wind blowing )
- ( Both gasp )

145
00:12:41,395 --> 00:12:46,166
Meruem: Whether it was a dream
or reality, I cannot say.

146
00:12:47,734 --> 00:12:49,669
And now...

147
00:12:49,736 --> 00:12:52,939
I cannot remember why i’m here.

148
00:12:54,842 --> 00:12:56,977
It escapes me.

149
00:12:57,044 --> 00:12:58,746
( Both groan )

150
00:13:03,584 --> 00:13:05,286
Shaiapouf: Lord meruem.

151
00:13:05,352 --> 00:13:07,921
Menthuthuyoupi:
You lost your memory?

152
00:13:07,988 --> 00:13:10,023
♪

153
00:13:10,090 --> 00:13:12,559
Meruem: I feel perfectly normal.

154
00:13:12,626 --> 00:13:17,097
In fact, I am absolutely
overflowing with raw energy.

155
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:24,104
My mind, however,
is clouded in fog.

156
00:13:26,607 --> 00:13:27,942
( Gasps )

157
00:13:28,008 --> 00:13:31,245
Tell me,
why do you look like that?

158
00:13:31,311 --> 00:13:32,779
( Menthuthuyoupi gasps )

159
00:13:33,914 --> 00:13:36,250
( Shaiapouf shudders )

160
00:13:36,316 --> 00:13:40,153
We both sent our segments out
to scout the area.

161
00:13:40,220 --> 00:13:43,757
They are searching for enemies
and will dispose--

162
00:13:43,824 --> 00:13:46,727
- ( gasps )
- ( Menthuthuyoupi gasps )

163
00:13:47,828 --> 00:13:49,263
Meruem: Hear me well,

164
00:13:49,329 --> 00:13:53,133
for I will not repeat myself.
Do you understand?

165
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:56,770
It makes no difference to me
if you do it out of affection.

166
00:13:56,837 --> 00:14:00,774
Lying to me
is a breach of trust.

167
00:14:05,179 --> 00:14:08,616
So I did eat you.

168
00:14:09,750 --> 00:14:11,719
I ate both of you.

169
00:14:11,785 --> 00:14:14,621
Shaiapouf: We offered ourselves
to you freely!

170
00:14:14,688 --> 00:14:16,990
Menthuthuyoupi: We know we
stepped way out of line, sire,

171
00:14:17,057 --> 00:14:18,792
but it’s what we really wanted.

172
00:14:22,796 --> 00:14:24,698
Meruem: Well, what happened?

173
00:14:24,765 --> 00:14:26,133
Explain yourselves.

174
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:28,302
Shaiapouf: Before we do,

175
00:14:28,368 --> 00:14:31,538
i’m afraid that I
must ask you a question.

176
00:14:31,605 --> 00:14:33,874
It appears that you
are able to recall

177
00:14:33,941 --> 00:14:36,277
our former appearances
quite well, my lord,

178
00:14:36,343 --> 00:14:38,979
and I wonder, do you remember

179
00:14:39,046 --> 00:14:41,148
the day that we first
began serving you?

180
00:14:43,217 --> 00:14:45,119
( Meruem sighs )

181
00:14:46,286 --> 00:14:48,755
No, I do not.

182
00:14:48,822 --> 00:14:51,124
I did, however, recognize

183
00:14:51,191 --> 00:14:53,894
that both of you
had been my royal guards.

184
00:14:53,961 --> 00:14:56,730
I knew your names
the moment I saw you.

185
00:14:56,797 --> 00:15:00,768
Perhaps I should say instead
that I remembered them,

186
00:15:00,834 --> 00:15:05,505
but as to how that came to be,
I cannot recall.

187
00:15:05,572 --> 00:15:07,207
Shaiapouf: My lord meruem...

188
00:15:08,976 --> 00:15:11,712
I think that you
may be suffering

189
00:15:11,778 --> 00:15:14,114
from memory loss
due to the explosion.

190
00:15:14,181 --> 00:15:16,250
Meruem: An explosion, you say?

191
00:15:16,316 --> 00:15:17,250
Shaiapouf: Yes.

192
00:15:18,986 --> 00:15:21,622
That’s why you came here,
you see,

193
00:15:21,688 --> 00:15:24,624
to engage in a duel
with the enemy.

194
00:15:24,691 --> 00:15:28,195
However, the human,
a coward and a scoundrel,

195
00:15:28,262 --> 00:15:31,265
resorted to a devious,
underhanded trick

196
00:15:31,331 --> 00:15:35,769
and utilized a powerful bomb,
betraying your good faith.

197
00:15:37,905 --> 00:15:39,273
♪

198
00:15:39,339 --> 00:15:44,578
Meruem: A duel.
Yes, that’s right.

199
00:15:44,645 --> 00:15:47,248
I remember it now.

200
00:15:47,314 --> 00:15:51,251
I was fighting a duel.

201
00:15:51,318 --> 00:15:54,822
Shaiapouf: But given your power
and your limitless fortune,

202
00:15:54,888 --> 00:15:59,559
we knew that a human would
never be able to kill you, sire.

203
00:15:59,626 --> 00:16:04,097
However, none of us could bear
to see you in that state,

204
00:16:04,164 --> 00:16:07,668
so we did what we could
to speed your recovery,

205
00:16:07,734 --> 00:16:10,670
knowing full well
that we might be punished.

206
00:16:13,574 --> 00:16:17,511
After all, sire,
our bodies are not our own.

207
00:16:17,578 --> 00:16:19,880
No, they belong entirely to you.

208
00:16:20,981 --> 00:16:22,182
We merely returned

209
00:16:22,249 --> 00:16:24,685
what was already yours
in the first place.

210
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:28,722
Menthuthuyoupi:
Let’s go back to the palace.

211
00:16:28,789 --> 00:16:30,724
( Shaiapouf gasps )

212
00:16:30,791 --> 00:16:32,926
Menthuthuyoupi:
That will be the fastest way

213
00:16:32,993 --> 00:16:34,895
for you to regain your memory.

214
00:16:37,164 --> 00:16:39,299
Shaiapouf: Well, well.

215
00:16:39,366 --> 00:16:43,904
This, this is
a golden opportunity!

216
00:16:45,205 --> 00:16:47,741
♪

217
00:16:47,808 --> 00:16:50,110
If I return
to the palace first...

218
00:16:51,812 --> 00:16:53,714
I can dispose of it.

219
00:16:55,115 --> 00:16:58,752
At the moment, the king
does not remember her.

220
00:16:58,819 --> 00:17:02,890
If I eliminate her now,
all of this is finished.

221
00:17:02,956 --> 00:17:05,959
He’ll never even remember
who she was.

222
00:17:09,129 --> 00:17:12,766
This will require
convincing pitou

223
00:17:12,833 --> 00:17:16,003
and getting rid
of that meddling human.

224
00:17:16,069 --> 00:17:19,806
No, I know what I must do.

225
00:17:19,873 --> 00:17:24,644
Before all else,
I must end its life.

226
00:17:25,879 --> 00:17:27,013
( Joints pop )

227
00:17:27,080 --> 00:17:29,082
If I can kill her,

228
00:17:29,149 --> 00:17:31,785
everything else
will fall into place.

229
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:35,055
If he’s running at full speed,

230
00:17:35,122 --> 00:17:39,226
the king will still need
20 minutes to reach the palace.

231
00:17:39,293 --> 00:17:43,197
Oh, that’s more
than enough time to kill her.

232
00:17:54,341 --> 00:17:56,643
Menthuthuyoupi: Whoa.

233
00:17:56,710 --> 00:17:58,712
Meruem: This feels as natural

234
00:17:58,779 --> 00:18:01,782
as if I were born
with these attached to my body.

235
00:18:01,849 --> 00:18:02,783
( Shaiapouf gasps )

236
00:18:02,850 --> 00:18:05,086
Meruem: I can already fly.

237
00:18:11,191 --> 00:18:13,493
- ( Shaiapouf gasps )
- ( Menthuthuyoupi laughs )

238
00:18:15,229 --> 00:18:16,831
Meruem: Which way to the palace?

239
00:18:16,897 --> 00:18:18,065
Menthuthuyoupi: North, sire.

240
00:18:18,131 --> 00:18:19,766
You should be able
to make it there

241
00:18:19,833 --> 00:18:22,035
in about 15 minutes or so
if you hurry up.

242
00:18:22,102 --> 00:18:24,037
( Wind blowing )

243
00:18:31,011 --> 00:18:32,246
Meruem: It’s there.

244
00:18:32,312 --> 00:18:34,247
Menthuthuyoupi: Huh?

245
00:18:34,314 --> 00:18:36,249
( Shaiapouf gasps )

246
00:18:36,316 --> 00:18:38,985
Meruem: I realize
the answer that I seek

247
00:18:39,052 --> 00:18:40,854
is there within the palace.

248
00:18:40,921 --> 00:18:43,257
♪

249
00:19:00,874 --> 00:19:02,075
Shaiapouf: He’s fast.

250
00:19:02,142 --> 00:19:04,645
I can’t slow down,
or he’ll catch up!

251
00:19:04,711 --> 00:19:06,580
Fifteen minutes? No.

252
00:19:06,647 --> 00:19:08,816
At this speed,
he’ll get there in five.

253
00:19:08,882 --> 00:19:10,684
There’s so little time to spare.

254
00:19:10,751 --> 00:19:13,854
Quickly! Quickly, my segments!

255
00:19:16,256 --> 00:19:17,657
This is a gamble.

256
00:19:19,026 --> 00:19:20,661
It won’t be long before the king

257
00:19:20,727 --> 00:19:23,897
sees the millions of humans
gathered outside the palace.

258
00:19:23,964 --> 00:19:26,266
Then he’ll remember everything.

259
00:19:27,801 --> 00:19:29,569
He’ll remember
that his objective

260
00:19:29,636 --> 00:19:32,539
is to rule over
all living creatures.

261
00:19:35,576 --> 00:19:38,245
That’s why
he cannot see that girl.

262
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:41,816
As a royal guard,

263
00:19:41,882 --> 00:19:45,819
as one who has inherited
the queen’s will...

264
00:19:45,886 --> 00:19:49,590
It’s my duty to eliminate
that lowly human girl.

265
00:19:54,828 --> 00:19:56,596
She’s gone.

266
00:19:58,165 --> 00:20:00,000
But where...

267
00:20:01,869 --> 00:20:03,070
Knuckle: Hakoware!

268
00:20:14,147 --> 00:20:17,083
Palm: I’ve seen you
with my eye before...

269
00:20:20,754 --> 00:20:24,691
Before I was
turned into a cocoon.

270
00:20:28,228 --> 00:20:30,964
That means i’ll always
be able to see you,

271
00:20:31,031 --> 00:20:33,066
no matter where you go.

272
00:20:37,004 --> 00:20:38,639
Shaiapouf: What was that?

273
00:20:38,705 --> 00:20:41,741
It felt like something
just attacked my segment.

274
00:20:41,808 --> 00:20:45,145
Whatever it was,
it came from nowhere.

275
00:20:45,212 --> 00:20:48,148
Meruem: What’s wrong?
Tell me what’s happening.

276
00:20:48,215 --> 00:20:49,583
Shaiapouf: Eh?

277
00:20:49,650 --> 00:20:51,152
( Gasps )

278
00:20:51,218 --> 00:20:55,022
I don’t know.
It seems to have resulted

279
00:20:55,088 --> 00:20:57,724
from the remaining enemies
attacking my segment.

280
00:20:59,126 --> 00:21:00,327
Meruem: Let us hurry.

281
00:21:10,037 --> 00:21:11,705
Palm: It’s the king.

282
00:21:11,772 --> 00:21:13,707
♪

283
00:21:21,281 --> 00:21:23,650
The king is alive!

284
00:21:24,852 --> 00:21:26,787
( Singing in Japanese )

